CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 7, 1958, pg. A12 reads: "Beantowners Meet Pittsburgher - Four Boston Gays surround Pittsburgh Gay, Miriam Bush, during the formal ball given Saturday night at eh Penn-Sheraton. From left: Lurlean Levister, Emily Lewis, Miss Bush, Viola Minor and Marjorie Phillibert."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of five Gay Northeasterner members, from left: Lurlean Levister, Emily Lewis, Miriam Bush, Viola Minor and Marjorie Phillibert, standing in Penn Sheraton Hotel for grand ball
